      <subfield code="a">Introduction : nature, choice and social power -- Mining : earth and water -- Mining nature -- Miners -- Why is gold valuable? -- The car and suburban sprawl : aie and fire -- Henry Ford's car -- Sprawl -- Los Angeles : a brief biography -- Conclusion : power, choice and nature.</subfield>
